{"tid":2292003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉因政見問題起爭執強吻男子 退休女警：信唔信再錫你多一下","createTime":"2020-11-19T07:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:32:13.000Z","uid":24050,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd28e022967ebd1414a0e59c219d638add63f80","tid":2292003,"uid":24050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:29:17.000Z","msg":"退休女警因政見問題與人爭執，期間疑不滿被拍攝而強吻一名年輕男子，又打向他用來拍攝的電話，被控非禮及兩項普通襲擊罪，今在西九龍裁判法院受審。事主供稱，他遭強吻後，被告一度揚言：「信唔信再錫你多一下！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主X供稱，去年9月5日晚上，他在長沙灣海麗邨海和樓公園，見到近百人聚集爭執，有人指控一名女子「打人」，並聲言已經報警，故阻止女子離開，他見狀上前掏出手機拍攝。被告吳葉淑芬（68歲）後來加入口角時，走近質問他為何要拍攝，他反問「影你係咪唔得？係咪犯法？」，被告繼而傾前「嘴對嘴咁錫咗我一啖」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nX馬上後退及抹嘴，他見被告想再哄前，遂用手推開她。被告之後繼續與人口角，X則再用手機拍攝。惟不久後，被告又再質問X 為何拍攝，更出手大力打向他的電話，撞到他的右臉，令他感到痛楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方不久後到場，將二人帶返警署。X在警署以普通襲擊罪被捕，指控他推開過被告，又問他願不願意與被告和解。X一口拒絕，數小時後獲准擔保候查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n庭上播放一段由在場人士拍攝的片段，當時群眾正等候警方到場，身穿深色碎花裙連身裙的被告向在場人士說：「差人係打曱甴嘅，蒙面嗰啲啊！」，旋即引起對罵。此時X站在一旁用手機拍攝，被告到他面前質問，再哄前用嘴碰他的嘴唇。在場人士隨即與被告理論，擾攘間被告大聲說：「我再錫添啊！」，說罷向X哄近，X則不停退後。X在庭上解釋，「我驚佢真係再錫我一吓」，故後退躲避。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告今由當值律師代表。他質疑X一早知悉被告及其丈夫都是警務人員，故當天拍攝是為了「起底」，又指被告只是意外碰到他的嘴唇，X不同意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：張旭珊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頭條唔貼link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e60b68eba98c0b9af9507dd8def938fd928dc5e","tid":2292003,"uid":136186,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c9cfe55ec8b235892bfe9cbfeec6cc64085793","tid":2292003,"uid":109629,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"成口驅風油......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f5136ed4590276ab91e70276539b0cf1b0a4a1","tid":2292003,"uid":74361,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"錫佢春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cb46d046080ca595f291221cb1881112cc6d8d","tid":2292003,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d4292c8a85a8579e277ec14d061b1e03b81e2b","tid":2292003,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"信唔信我幫你口爆啦"},{"pid":"5c6bbed8a9bf739506fa025e236b411f5aa1d461","tid":2292003,"uid":61974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"老殻閪想乘機抽後生仔水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458185d0a06bf0a189f1cbcd562f36c263491246","tid":2292003,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"搜查官系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7b57540abc1b873484bf0a14c94a1b86b3b90a","tid":2292003,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d4292c8a85a8579e277ec14d061b1e03b81e2b","tid":2292003,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"信唔信我幫你口爆啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"煙屎口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4261cba5c2b8b